title: Sorin Botiș
text:
Sorin Botiş (born 14 April 1978 in <a href="Arad%2C%20Romania">Arad</a>) is a retired <a href="Romanian%20people">Romanian</a> <a href="association%20football">football</a> player.
Club career.
Ferencvárosi TC.
He made his debut on 2 August 2003 against <a href="Videoton%20FC%20Feh%C3%A9rv%C3%A1r">Videoton FC Fehérvár</a> in a match that ended 2–2.
Zalaegerszegi TE.
He made his debut on 31 July 2006 against <a href="Videoton%20FC%20Feh%C3%A9rv%C3%A1r">Videoton FC Fehérvár</a> in a match that ended 3–2.
Budapest Honved.
He made his debut on 25 July 2009 against <a href="Kaposv%C3%A1ri%20R%C3%A1k%C3%B3czi%20FC">Kaposvári Rákóczi FC</a> in a match that ended 3–1.
